    <h1>12 BEST BUYS AT JEWELUXE 2020</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201204/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-12-04"><time>2020-12-04</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>8</p>
    <p>MOUAWAD LOVE M RING ($5,500)</p>
    <p>Four hearts come to­gether in this 0.54-carat ring from Le­banon-founded her­itage brand Mouawad, held to­gether by a di­a­mond cen­tre­piece. JeweLuxe founder An­gela Loh says: “The four hearts, to me, sym­bol­ise ro­man­tic love, fam­ily love, love of friends and most im­por­tantly, self love.”</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: Mouawad at Paragon</p>
    <p>9</p>
    <p>P&P JEW­ELLERY GOLDEN SOUTH SEA PEARL EAR­RINGS (PRICE UPON RE­QUEST)</p>
    <p>Sym­bol­is­ing pro­tec­tion and the idea of an­gels walk­ing among us, the mo­tif of an­gel wings ap­pears fre­quently on P&P Jew­ellery’s pieces – in­clud­ing this pair of 18-karat yel­low gold ear­rings fea­tur­ing two 12.3mm golden South Sea pearls and 14 pieces of di­a­monds.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: The Di­a­mond Ate­lier by Lee Hwa Jew­ellery at VivoCity from Dec 15</p>
    <p>10 NIESSING MI­RAGE PEN­DANTS (FROM $1,998)</p>
    <p>Take your pick of 18-karat rose gold, yel­low gold and white gold with Ger­man jew­eller Niessing’s Mi­rage pen­dants, which fea­ture a play of tex­tures on the pre­cious met­als.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: Lee Hwa Di­a­mond Prom­e­nade at Ion Or­chard, The Di­a­mond Ate­lier by Lee Hwa Jew­ellery at VivoCity and Lee Hwa Jew­ellery at Great World</p>
    <p>11</p>
    <p>CARATELL ENAMEL CLOVER LEAF EAR­RINGS ($2,850)</p>
    <p>Get lucky with Caratell’s 18-karat white-and yel­low-gold four-leaf clover ear­rings. The new re­lease from lo­cal jew­eller Michael Koh – embellishe­d with eight di­a­monds and eight ru­bies – high­lights the tra­di­tional craft of enam­elling. Avail­able at: Caratell at 20 Handy Road</p>
    <p>12</p>
    <p>OPHION RA­DIAL RED WATCH</p>
    <p>(PRICE UPON RE­QUEST) Cus­tom-made ex­clu­sively for JeweLuxe 2020, this lim­ited-edi­tion watch fea­tures a strik­ing red brushed dial and a watch case by Vouti­lainen & Cat­tin SA. Only 55 pieces are avail­able for pur­chase.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: Watch Wonderland at Sun­tec City, North Wing</p>

